{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "禽子再拜再拜曰：", "text_normalized": "禽子再拜再拜曰：", "canonical_ref": "43.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "「敢問適人積土為高，以臨吾城，薪土俱上，以為羊黔，蒙櫓俱前，遂屬之城，兵弩俱上，為之柰何？", "text_normalized": "「敢問適人積土為高，以臨吾城，薪土俱上，以為羊黔，蒙櫓俱前，遂屬之城，兵弩俱上，為之柰何？", "canonical_ref": "43.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "」", "text_normalized": "」", "canonical_ref": "43.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "43.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "「子問羊黔之守邪？", "text_normalized": "「子問羊黔之守邪？", "canonical_ref": "43.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "羊黔者將之拙者也，足以勞卒，不足以害城。", "text_normalized": "羊黔者將之拙者也，足以勞卒，不足以害城。", "canonical_ref": "43.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "守為臺城，以臨羊黔，左右出巨，各二十尺，行城三十尺，強弩射之，技機藉之，奇器口口之，然則羊黔之攻敗矣。", "text_normalized": "守為臺城，以臨羊黔，左右出巨，各二十尺，行城三十尺，強弩射之，技機藉之，奇器口口之，然則羊黔之攻敗矣。", "canonical_ref": "43.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "備臨以連弩之車材大方一方一尺，長稱城之薄厚。", "text_normalized": "備臨以連弩之車材大方一方一尺，長稱城之薄厚。", "canonical_ref": "43.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "兩軸三輪，輪居筐中，重下上筐。", "text_normalized": "兩軸三輪，輪居筐中，重下上筐。", "canonical_ref": "43.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "左右旁二植，左右有衡植，衡植左右皆圜內，內徑四寸。", "text_normalized": "左右旁二植，左右有衡植，衡植左右皆圜內，內徑四寸。", "canonical_ref": "43.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "左右縳弩皆於植，以弦鉤弦，至於大弦。", "text_normalized": "左右縳弩皆於植，以弦鉤弦，至於大弦。", "canonical_ref": "43.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "弩臂前後與筐齊，筐高八尺，弩軸去下筐三尺五寸。", "text_normalized": "弩臂前後與筐齊，筐高八尺，弩軸去下筐三尺五寸。", "canonical_ref": "43.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "連弩機郭同銅，一石三十鈞。", "text_normalized": "連弩機郭同銅，一石三十鈞。", "canonical_ref": "43.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "引弦鹿長奴。", "text_normalized": "引弦鹿長奴。", "canonical_ref": "43.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "筐大三圍半，左右有鉤距，方三寸，輪厚尺二寸，鉤距臂博尺四寸，厚七寸，長六尺。", "text_normalized": "筐大三圍半，左右有鉤距，方三寸，輪厚尺二寸，鉤距臂博尺四寸，厚七寸，長六尺。", "canonical_ref": "43.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "橫臂齊筐外，蚤尺五寸，有距，博六寸，厚三寸，長如筐，有儀，有詘勝，可上下。", "text_normalized": "橫臂齊筐外，蚤尺五寸，有距，博六寸，厚三寸，長如筐，有儀，有詘勝，可上下。", "canonical_ref": "43.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "為武重一石以材大圍五寸。", "text_normalized": "為武重一石以材大圍五寸。", "canonical_ref": "43.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "矢長十尺，以繩系箭矢端，如如戈射，以磿鹿卷收。", "text_normalized": "矢長十尺，以繩系箭矢端，如如戈射，以磿鹿卷收。", "canonical_ref": "43.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "矢高弩臂三尺，用弩無數，出人六十枚，用小矢無留。", "text_normalized": "矢高弩臂三尺，用弩無數，出人六十枚，用小矢無留。", "canonical_ref": "43.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "十人主此車。", "text_normalized": "十人主此車。", "canonical_ref": "43.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation", "source_id": "mozi-043-defense-against-attack-from-an-elevation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "遂具寇，為高樓以射道，城上以荅、羅，矢。", "text_normalized": "遂具寇，為高樓以射道，城上以荅、羅，矢。", "canonical_ref": "43.21", "notes": ""}
